{"type": "article", "id": 54129, "title": "一口气出8款特别款手工地毯，宜家这次跨界挺活跃｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-06-10T23:05:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 13757, "name": "Bang & Olufsen"}, {"id": 50986, "name": "Palomba Serafini Associati"}, {"id": 50987, "name": "Primitive Skateboarding"}, {"id": 302, "name": "宜家"}, {"id": 50988, "name": "Junbyung Choi"}, {"id": 50989, "name": "Leon Faust"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 120, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180610222659tKJky8ewqXNPOrz3.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #337ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #337ab7} span.s5 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>IKEA ART RUGS 2019 by Virgil Abloh，Craig Green，Supakitch，Chiaozza，Noah Lyon，Seulgi Lee，Misaki Kawai &amp; Filip Pagowski </h3><p>在上周的第 5 届 IKEA 民主设计体验日上，IKEA Art Event 2019 项目也一并亮相。今年宜家请来了 Virgil Abloh、Craig Green、Supakitch、Chiaozza、Noah Lyon、Seulgi Lee、Misaki Kawai 和 Filip Pagowski 八位设计师和艺术家助阵，以地毯为主题展开创作。</p><p>所有地毯都是用羊毛与自然材质手工制作而成，因此每一块地毯都可以说是独一无二。除了早前曝光的 Virgil Abloh 的 “KEEP OFF” 和 “STILL LOADING”，英国时装设计师 Craig Green 的设计是同名品牌 2018 春夏系列的延续，日本艺术家 Misaki Kawai 带来充满趣味的“狮子家庭”，Filip Pagowski 的作品是如钩针编织般的繁复设计等等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806102227403tcD1kEipqJePgVA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610222740bpqVZyG4RWP78cer.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610222740fVKAQMNGnvqzI5H7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610222740GSRCFBmZV2vuLpnj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610222740w6Qrs5iEXvlUgtxC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610222740VOqf0L1WudX3cD4k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018061022274085i46k31YuVKAzZL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>KODO by Leon Faust</h3><p>就读于新加坡莱佛士设计学院产品设计系的毕业生 Leon Faust，毕业作品是一个名为 KODO 的便携式烧烤架，灵感来源于中国传统的腰鼓。在设计师看来，烧烤这个行为本身有一种原始狂野的色彩，就像鼓一样。正如这个产品，它并不告诉你应该如何生活，它只提供一个视角，把烧烤视为一种仪式，对平常无聊平淡生活的割裂。</p><p>KODO 的目标用户是年轻一代。生火的方式类似于引火桶，不至于让人生火时不知所措。然后中间的部分可以放些烧烤的配件。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=d06849alp60&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610222809ZWsmel13GH8DFtRE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610222809e75FBAtSUqblONjk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800853\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610222809v9MsAhVUopDO2Gwe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707116\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610222810uiZWxDoXABm1Mcsh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Leon Faust<p><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 54, 54); font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><br></span></p><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 54, 54); font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">Primitive Skateboarding x Rick and Morty</span></h3></figcaption></figure></div><p>来自南加州的滑板品牌 Primitive Skateboarding，最近以美国电视科幻情景喜剧动画《瑞克和莫蒂》（Rick and Morty）为主题，推出了一系列联名单品，包括 T 恤、卫衣、外套、帽子等等。整个系列结合了动画角色中的经典形象，并且选择以蓝色、紫色、黄色、粉色和绿色为主调，甚至将扎染元素融入其中。</p><p>除此之外，该系列的配饰设计也很醒目，包括 Rick 和 Morty 两人“拼接”而成的滑板，绿色夜光时钟，以及袜子、水杯和 Yo-yo 球等趣味设计。售价 27.95 美元起，<a href=\"https://primitiveskate.com/collections/rick-and-morty\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610222946wso3dJ2zXVuGFfeq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610222946zEUM7HwPcqVSxhNr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610222946tMhmXZbp1C8DLy2j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610222946XTOibIeaHEz3FjtM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610222946bF1hZV2sIa5DKR80.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666107\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610222946X6vFDxdZS0gwVjCc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610222946wQWlR6tNZ5S4EY8b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610222946GkUzXwjWybho4Dcd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Egret Lounge Chair by PS+A</h3><p>米兰设计工作室 Palomba Serafini Associati 最近为家居设计品牌造作设计了一款名为鹭鸶的躺椅。设计师以纤细而轻扬的笔画，构想白鹭轻灵身姿，纤腿、翅翼与蓑羽，以金属与曲木意像呈现，步态婀娜。碧灰格、灰白格两色座椅，每款均以经纬 2 种色线编织，面料以涤纶与腈纶等量混纺，触感柔韧且耐磨耐脏，兼备抗皱抗菌的耐久性。</p><p>它可以用作沙发区的座位补充，为空间点缀极致简练的线条美感。也可以与落地灯搭配，在角落搭起独处的阅读区。售价 1399 元，<a href=\"https://www.zaozuo.com/item/300220\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610223020jdwXG1UxgfklS3oE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610223020EeNg8D76hWIX5VTL.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610223020Ph7nVEUArMoDe1Ws.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806102230215ZiAz1prNehRQDtK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610223021tdo06u9FJLrzDbcO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>BeoVision Eclipse &amp; BeoLab 50 by Bang &amp; Olufsen</h3><p>丹麦高端音响品牌 Bang &amp; Olufsen 最近更新了旗下两款产品的设计，包括 BeoVision Eclipse 电视机和 BeoLab 50 扬声器。相较于旧版本，新版本增添了黄铜色和烟熏橡木两种细节，为硬朗的高科技产品添入了不少北欧美学特征。</p><p>BeoVision Eclipse 在电动座地脚架及 SoundCentre 的侧面和背面覆盖了黄铜色铝材，甚至连遥控器也采用了黄铜色铝材设计，而扬声器的外罩更是用烟熏橡木手工制作而成。BeoLab 50 也换上了黄铜色饰面，经过阳极氧化处理，呈现出复古质感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610223043UIDzdwF3OHWTM5kv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610223043dUqE3lRVTBubZn8H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018061022304375XuwcV8Cn6elByW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667179\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610223044EN05GLV4ZJvi2UKp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Objet by Junbyung Choi</h3><p>吹风机的收纳一直都是个麻烦事儿。不如直接把它吸在墙上？设计师 Junbyung Choi 设计的这款吹风机 Objet 可以吸附在墙壁上，便于整理你的卫生间，很贴心的设计。中性色与简洁结构的结合，使得 Objet 可以与任意室内装饰风格轻松融合。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610223120SLuEinKvXHFfZAaN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610223120pY9Ak7qvIizL2RBf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610223120myfVx9rMg8ckb0KP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610223120m97ns3VTqfbQUkRY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610223120oIHXlWYNqE8f4eZ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610223120eVwqUzRAMusfChal.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180610223121KJQrnOgiAeaZ6uP3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/06/08/a-truly-practical-hairdryer/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}